Class PortableMediaCreatorPlugin.HTMLTable

java.lang.Object
  de.iftm.dcm4che.router.plugin.PortableMediaCreatorPlugin.HTMLTable
Enclosing class:
PortableMediaCreatorPlugin
protected class PortableMediaCreatorPlugin.HTMLTable
extends java.lang.Object

The objects of this class represent a HTML table. The objects support appending new rows and sorting the rows depending of the row attribute "title".
This class uses the inner class TableRowsComparator.
